                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>About FC Ordabasy</h3>
                    <p>Founded in 1998, FC Ordabasy is a professional football club based in Shymkent, Kazakhstan. The
                        club represents the city at the national level and is committed to sporting excellence.</p>
                    <p>Club achievements include winning the Kazakhstan Premier League title in 2022, the Kazakhstan Cup
                        in 2011 and 2023, and the Kazakhstan Super Cup in 2023.</p>
                    <button class="btn" onclick="toggleSection('history')">FULL HISTORY</button>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>Stadium</h3>
                    <p>Central Stadium in Shymkent has been the home of FC Ordabasy since the club's founding. With a
                        capacity of 20,000, it provides one of the best football atmospheres in Kazakhstan.</p>
                    <p>The stadium underwent major renovations in 2018 and now meets all UEFA standards for
                        international competitions.</p>
                    <button class="btn" onclick="toggleSection('stadium-tours')">STADIUM TOURS</button>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>Club Philosophy</h3>
                    <p>FC Ordabasy is committed to developing local talent while competing at the highest level. Our
                        philosophy combines modern football tactics with respect for traditional values.</p>
                    <p>The club focuses on youth development, community engagement, and building a sustainable football
                        culture in Shymkent and the surrounding regions.</p>
                    <button class="btn" onclick="toggleSection('values')">OUR VALUES</button>
